snippet.title: Europa - Official Release Date Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description:
Explore the gorgeous setting of Europa, and learn more about the story in this latest trailer for the upcoming adventure game ahead of its release on PC on April 16, 2024. A demo is also available now on Steam.


On the moon Europa, a lush terraformed paradise in Jupiter’s shadow, an android named Zee sets out in search of answers. Run, glide, and fly across the landscape, solve mysteries in the ruins of a fallen utopia, and discover the story of the last human alive.
